channel.title: Elvis Duran Phone Taps
channel.itunes:subtitle: Elvis Duran Phone Taps
channel.description: Elvis Duran Phone Taps is the ultimate podcast for prank call lovers! Get ready for the most outrageous, hilarious, and jaw-dropping phone taps from Elvis Duran and the Morning Show. Every episode features the show’s legendary prank calls, where the team has a blast messing with unsuspecting victims. From outrageous scenarios to clever twists, each phone tap is guaranteed to make you laugh out loud. Tune in and hear how Elvis and the crew pull off the perfect pranks—one laugh at a time!
